Exercice : Objets Littéraux

[ 'Hello, Dave'               => a ByteString
[1.3                          => a SmallFloat64
[#node1                       => a ByteSymbol
[#(2 33 4)                    => an Array
[ [ :each | each scale: 1.5]  => BlockClosure
[$A                           => a Character
[true                         => a True
[1                            => a SmallInteger


Exercice : Messages

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Expression                                   |  objet receiveur | selecteur du message | argument(s)        | resultat retourné 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[3 + 4                                       |         3        |          +           |     4              |    7
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Date today                                  |      Date        |    today             |                    |"14 January 2021"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[anArray at: 1 put:'hello'                   |     an Array     |      at,put          | 1, 'hello'         | 'hello'
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[anArray at: i                               |      an Array    |          at          |     i              |l'ieme element du tableau
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[#(2 33 -4 67) collect: [ :each | each abs ] |  #(2 33 -4 67)   |      collect         |[:each | each abs ] |   "#(2 33 4 67)"
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[25 @ 50           (Binary)                  |       25         |        @             |     50             |   "(25@50)"
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[ SmallInteger maxVal                        |  SmallInteger    | maxVal               |                    |"1152921504606846975"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[ #(a b c d e f ) includesAll: #(f d b)      | #(a b c d e f )  |   includesAll        |   #(f d b)          |   "true"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[true | false                                | true             |        |             |     false           |  "true" 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Point selectors                             |   Point          |     selectors        |                     | donne tout les methodes de la classe Point


Exercice : Nommage :

une variable nommée Transferator : on peut assumer que c'est une variable instance d'une classe Transfer (dans pharo il ya TransferModel TransferMorph et TransferPresenter)

une variable nommée rectangle : c'est peut etre une variable instance d'une classe Rectangle





